::Bobertron/Pantron::

    Bobertron paced the floor. He waited patiently for pantron's returned 
from his journey. Pantron entered through the door and had a look of caution 
on his face.
     "Howdy! I searched for the key. I figured out your riddle and found the 
key. Unfortunatly it was destroyed by the predacon Megatron. I suggest we 
take quick action to take vengence." Bobertron's optics glowed into a furious 
red. 
    "How did this happen. You now how important that was! How did he get the 
key off you!?"
    "He caught me from behind. He snatched it so a recieved little damage by 
running scared."
   "Lets go. Tell Magmatron what has happen and im sure he'll agree. Send a 
full force attack on Megatron.!"
